content: 0xbryer: Contributed two merged PRs this month: a documentation fix for a Thai text typo in PR #4116 (+1/-1 lines) and a chore optimization in PR #3900 that improved the cleanup script with `xargs` (+51353/-23949 lines). Activity was sporadic, being active on only 2 days this month. Contributions were evenly split between bugfix and refactoring work, with half of the changes focused on documentation.
